name: Why Didn't You Tell Me? (V)
Lore: 'Lacking foresight, Luke suffered the consequences of rushing into battle unprepared.',
Text: 'During any draw phase, place a card from hand under your Used Pile to take any one card into hand from Force Pile; reshuffle.  OR  Place IL-19 in owner''s Used Pile.  OR  During the power segment, cancel a just drawn destiny (except battle destiny).',
